These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, orange
House: tower, futuristic
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
2 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg
1. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the tower house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Food       | orange       | cabbage |
| House         | futuristic | tower  |
| Sport       | volleyball    | soccer    |
| Game   | mah-jongg       | canasta      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
House: craftsman, gothic-revival
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, video-games
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, reggae
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the fan of funk##1
2. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| House           | craftsman | gothic-revival      |
| Hobby   | video-games  | singing      |
| Music-Genre         | funk | reggae     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different games are played: scrabble, chess
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, lilac
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, country
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, zombie
1. the fan of country is on the left of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing scrabble is the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the person who likes apricot is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Game      | scrabble | chess  |
| Color          | apricot    | lilac   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   |
| Movie-Genre     | zombie     | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, documentary
There 2 different types of food: lemon, papaya
2 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, rugby
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Movie-Genre      | martial-arts       | documentary |
| Food          | papaya         | lemon    |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | cat    |
| Sport   | parkour           | rugby   |

 #################################

 
