.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-10::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, havana
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, polish
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod
1. the polish is the cape-cod house##1
2. the havana-smoker is on the right of the designer##1
3. the polish is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Job          | designer | dressmaker |
| Cigar   | davidoff     | havana      |
| Nationality   | malaysian | polish    |
| House           | gothic-revival    | cape-cod    |

