.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-18::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, september
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, kiwi
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bongani
2 different games are played: whist, domino
1. the aristoff-smoker is the person eating kiwi##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person playing domino##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Birthday      | february        | september        |
| Food          | grapefruit | kiwi       |
| Cigar         | bongani    | aristoff |
| Game   | domino    | whist  |

