The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, writing
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the japanese##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
