.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, security-guard
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, folk
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, february
House: craftsman, palace
1. the coach is on the right of the fan of soul##1
2. the coach is on the right of the palace house##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | security-guard | coach     |
| Music-Genre   | soul          | folk |
| Birthday           | july          | february    |
| House     | palace            | craftsman       |

 